1. *Pogledajte* kako se ova biljka predivno uklopila u enterijer. (Look* at* how this plant fits perfectly into the interior.) 
2. Nadam se da ćete uskoro *pogledati* moju izložbu slika. (I hope you'll come *to see* my art exhibition soon.)
3. Da li ste *pogledali* novi film koji je sinoć izašao? (Did you *watch* the new movie that came out last night?)
4. Kada *pogledate* fotografije, videćete koliko smo se lepo proveli. (When you *look at* the photos, you'll see how much fun we had.)
5. Moramo *pogledati* raspored za sutrašnji dan. (We need to *check* the schedule for tomorrow.)
6. *Pogledajmo* malo bolje ovaj problem da bismo našli rešenje. (Let's *take a closer look* at this problem to find a solution.)
7. Ukoliko ne *pogledate* preko ramena, nećete videti ko vam dolazi iza leđa. (If you don't *look over* your shoulder, you won't see who's coming up behind you.)
8. Oni su odlučili da *pogledaju* film kod kuće umesto da idu u bioskop. (They decided to *watch* the movie at home instead of going to the cinema.)
9. Ne mogu da *pogledam* u tu stranu jer me jako boli vrat. (I can't *turn my head* that way because my neck hurts.)
10. Kada *pogledate* celu situaciju iz ovog ugla, možda ćete videti drugačije rešenje. (When you *look at* the whole situation from this angle, you might see a different solution.)